This is a couple of months old.

00:51:51.000 --> 00:51:52.300
We're actually, actually
a little bit better now,

00:51:52.300 --> 00:51:53.950 position:56%
actually below the LISA requirement.

00:51:53.950 --> 00:51:55.250
So it was just incredible

00:51:55.250 --> 00:51:57.330
because not only did we meet
our requirements and exceed it

00:51:57.330 --> 00:51:59.870
by quite a bit, but we
basically are ready to do LISA

00:51:59.870 --> 00:52:02.800
and that's the main
