particular frequency

00:59:23.800 --> 00:59:26.790
and it has this particular
encoding of the information.

00:59:26.790 --> 00:59:28.590
That's what the numerical
relativity gets you.

00:59:28.590 --> 00:59:32.680
It says, I have this template
for a wave form and basically

00:59:32.680 --> 00:59:34.490
if I have multiple signals
